description: Veteran owned and family operated, Tin Hut BBQ is bringing something fantastic to the streets of Honolulu! The Diaz family is doing it right, combining together years of experience in the culinary world, the business world, and especially the BBQ world. A certified portable kitchen serving mainland BBQ on the island is something you don't see every day, so don't miss out on the incredible Tin Hut BBQ!
name: Tin Hut BBQ
